On page 126, in line 30, strike “1,759,507” and replace with “1,859,507”.
Updates the detail for the special fund appropriation for R30B36 University System of
Maryland Office, consistent with Item 58 of this Supplemental Budget.
Amendment No. 4:
On page 148, in line 18, strike “5,000,000” and replace with “10,000,000”, in line 21,
